relevant_findings.HEENT: Extraocular movements intact (EOMI), pupils equal, round, reactive to light (PERRL), moist mucous membranes (MMM)
relevant_findings.cardiac: Regular rate and rhythm (RRR), normal S1/S2, no murmurs, gallops, or rubs
relevant_findings.lung: Clear to auscultation bilaterally (CTAB), no wheezes, rales, or rhonchi, breathing comfortably without use of accessory muscles
relevant_findings.abdomen: Nondistended, positive bowel sounds (+BS), tender to palpation (TTP) in epigastric region without rebound or guarding
relevant_findings.skin: Warm and well perfused, no excoriations or lesions, no rashes
